<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Db_Statement currently supports:
fetchAll, fetchColumn, fetchObject</p>

<p>while Zend_Db_Adapter_Abstract:
fetchAll, fetchAssoc, fetchCol, fetchPairs, fetchOne, fetchRow</p>

<p>The method names should be unified (ie fetchColumn and fetchCol) and all methods should exist in both classes. Currently it's counter-intuitive.</p>

